    • returnNormalizedData

      public static final RowData returnNormalizedData(RowData data)
      Normalize the data so that most of the variables are within [-0.5,0.5] range. Using Zenko, 2007 suggestion. Should not be used with GD optimization - it has an internal normalization.

    • normalizeDataAndWriteToFile
